      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 28 letter about suppressed documentaries, which referred incorrectly to reason John Huston's Report From the Aleutians was banned; letter writer was told that Huston inadvertently showed classified bomb sight, not bomb site (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, a letter to the editor on May 28 about suppressed documentaries referred incorrectly to the reason John Huston's ''Report From the Aleutians'' was banned. The letter writer was told that Huston had inadvertently showed a classified bomb sight, not bomb site.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
